35859", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2064562655856381952/sHaMMrv8_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Freyja1 \ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc65\udb40\udc6e\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc7f\ud83c\uddf8\ud83c\uddef\ud83c\udde9\ud83c\uddea\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddea\ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc73\udb40\udc63\udb40\udc74\udb40\udc7f", "username": "FreyjaBakke"}, "content": "The 11-year-old French girl, Lyhanna, who was raped and BEATEN to death two weeks ago by a known offender in France?\n\nIt gets worse.\n\nAccording to information that has just been released, US authorities had already warned France about this man three months earlier.\n\nAnd this was", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 11137}}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f MURDEROUS LEFT \ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f\ud83d\udd25", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASswadAJi", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 71, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8683296, "raw_content": "Be me, never had a car that wasn't 5++ years old.\n\nJust bought a nicer low-mileage 3 y/o vehicle. Won't start, dead in driveway.\n\nBorrow a code reader from auto parts store. (free w/ deposit)\n\nUse Grok to diagnose codes. (free from work)\n\nGrok points out the part is covered under a manufacturer extended warranty thingy. (free repair)\n\nGet it towed to a dealership. (free)\n\nI don't know if it will take more than a day to repair, but if so, I will probably get a loaner vehicle. (free)\n\nThe moral of this story is that God is great Frens. Put your faith in Him and do not worry. Everything always works out. It always does.", "author": "kek-is-tan", "created": 1781617002608, "profile_picture": "I8XXB1DBtIOB", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "LokeyLewd", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user":